{"tid":1853812,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[攬炒］金管局：根據銀行信息　料約20-30%分行暫時關閉","createTime":"2020-01-31T07:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T11:32:47.000Z","uid":32323,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b5358d08ddec85d6b2f7489365a9a85d5b018392","tid":1853812,"uid":32323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:24:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505860-20200131.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505860-20200131.htm&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik67%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=f91b1c21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505860-20200131.htm&h=2a7f80cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505860-20200131.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n金管局發言人表示，為減低新型冠狀病毒疫情擴散，並加強對員工及客戶的保障，銀行業已經採取一系列措施，包括實施分隔工作安排，以及允許員工在可行情況下留在家中工作。<br />\n<br />\n金管局收到銀行匯報，為了在以上基礎上繼續營運，部分銀行分行須暫時關閉或縮短營業時間。根據銀行提供的信息，預計約20-30%分行暫時關閉，其餘繼續運作的分行中，部分縮短營業時間，各銀行會盡快公布具體營運安排。<br />\n<br />\n金管局建議銀行客戶盡量使用網上或電話銀行、自動櫃員機或其他電子銀行服務，希望公眾諒解銀行因應目前特殊公共衛生情況而作出的臨時安排。<br />\n<br />\n金管局將密切留意疫情發展，與業界保持緊密溝通，銀行會不斷檢視是否需要進一步調整分行營運安排。"},{"pid":"a324a2574a3845eb64bb0fc07ffc15f826709db8","tid":1853812,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:25:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">抗疫不忘抗爭</span></span><br />\n希望大家幫p牌推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解答到 國際關係 海洋法庭制裁警暴<br />\n呢啲議題 <br />\n唔好比肺炎spin開左 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地仲未光復到香港！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一齊收港共支共皮</span><br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉高汁分析 點光復香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1853544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1853544</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9df6c10d50d8fda3a64a3a79e4dbe565c1430b04","tid":1853812,"uid":32323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c8f86d1210f733f528b3d2d148a08c16202da1","tid":1853812,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:28:44.000Z","msg":"倒閉"},{"pid":"c41a791049969f70f31d40a0866bf6a5ebd9b19d","tid":1853812,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96bae306d5fc4ad9ac9c2bdf6ed505fbf9f8d264","tid":1853812,"uid":276274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:30:27.000Z","msg":"藍絲準備換鞋去踢爆匯豐分行啲門"},{"pid":"e2279e5d63e47dfe534f1337513cf573f043e845","tid":1853812,"uid":34517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:32:00.000Z","msg":"屌 會唔會嚇到啲啊伯啊婆以為執笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03cff977de6a8d1823740cefc71fc9674301446","tid":1853812,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:50:26.000Z","msg":"狗衝落去攞錢"},{"pid":"63b4d92346ff29cf23c8f253eb2570d58d890a96","tid":1853812,"uid":32323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:54:53.000Z","msg":"中銀49間，2月1日起"},{"pid":"56a3a0f537d94bc7742e83b5280cd4536095e50f","tid":1853812,"uid":32323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:02:36.000Z","msg":"恒生31間"},{"pid":"62d75507265822998e807e9460d7e80b78118c1f","tid":1853812,"uid":283442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96bae306d5fc4ad9ac9c2bdf6ed505fbf9f8d264","tid":1853812,"uid":276274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:30:27.000Z","msg":"藍絲準備換鞋去踢爆匯豐分行啲門"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class